an sign-off and confirm the release decision before handing to DevOps.","inputArtifactId":"Human Approval Packet","outputArtifactId":"Approval Decision Record","approverRoles":["Development Manager","Squad Leader","Team Lead"],"exitCriteria":["Human approval captured","Release decision documented","Deployment cleared to proceed"],"templatePath":"/out/steps/human-approval-template.md","allowedToolIds":[],"executionNotes":"This step always pauses for explicit human approval. The backend runner must not auto-complete it.","artifactContract":{"requiredInputs":["Human Approval Packet","Release Readiness Record","Rollback Plan","Release Window Details"],"expectedOutputs":["Approval Decision Record","Release Authorization","Approver Comments Log"],"notes":"Human approval should capture a durable authorization record and any release conditions or comments."}},{"id":"STEP-CAPABILITYIDTOKEN-8","name":"Release Execution","type":"RELEASE","phase":"RELEASE","layout":{"x":2160,"y":928},"agentId":"AGENT-CAPABILITYIDTOKEN-DEVOPS","action":"Deploy, verify, and close the release.","description":"Execute deployment, verify the release, and publish the final operational status.","inputArtifactId":"Deployment Authorization Packet","outputArtifactId":"Deployment Summary","exitCriteria":["Deployment completed","Operational verification passed","Release summary published"],"templatePath":"/out/steps/release-step-template.md","allowedToolIds":["workspace_read","git_status","run_deploy","run_docs"],"executionNotes":"Release execution can only use capability-configured deployment/doc commands and must remain approval-gated before deployment starts.","artifactContract":{"requiredInputs":["Deployment Authorization Packet","Release Authorization","Deployment Plan","Rollback Plan"],"expectedOutputs":["Deployment Summary","Production Verification Report","Release Notes","Hypercare Handoff"],"notes":"Release execution should leave behind a complete operational record of what was deployed and how it